ateX(0) rotateY(0) rotate(0) skew(0,0)\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-14\"><div data-w-id=\"7d26cb82-e8d9-67d0-70f7-b35423b59d94\" class=\"div-block-8-2copy\"></div></a> <div data-w-id=\"7d26cb82-e8d9-67d0-70f7-b35423b59d95\" class=\"div-block-5-copy\"><img src=\"/362dd6b6f94a40e7b6d35bbaeeb0eea6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-38\"> <p class=\"paragraph-copy-copy-copy\">Exploring UX design of a text-on-path feature for mobile devices<br></p> </div><img src=\"/a402e2a3ca303a8a27eeb63a8bbf49e0.png\" data-w-id=\"7d26cb82-e8d9-67d0-70f7-b35423b59d9c\" style=\"opacity:0\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-13\"></div> <div class=\"section-6\"> <div class=\"div-b0lock-9-copy\"> <div data-w-id=\"1ac9e762-0c3e-9a37-0406-b9684d357500\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-3-copy\"> <h1 class=\"heading-2-copy2-copy\">Background</h1> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy\"><em>Text on Path</em> is a popular and useful functionality in photo editing software. It lets you control the path of the text. This feature is missing in mobile editing apps.<br>‍<br>In this project, I looked into new user experiences that are easy to use on-the-go. After researching the subject, I created 3 main concepts.<br></p> </div> <div data-w-id=\"a2266cf1-07a8-ef16-ef74-2c849d279792\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-11\"><img src=\"/a8b88e48058ef7534fbbabdd5498fd13.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-22\"></div> <p class=\"paragraph-4\">Text on path example on Photoshop</p> <div data-w-id=\"cd33958c-1cab-b44b-685b-4a32b2b1d00f\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-3-copy\"> <h1 class=\"heading-2-copy2-copy\">Concept 1: Drawing the path</h1> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy\">Drawing the path using your finger while swiping it on the screen.</p> </div> <div data-w-id=\"e8b288a7-8ace-6d34-64e2-b5c7eea3d2e1\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"html-embed-2 w-embed w-iframe\"> <div class=\"center\"> <iframe onload=\"delayedLoad()\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"100%\" max-width=\"700px\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.figma.com/embed?embed_host=share&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.figma.com%2Ffile%2FLq9hebNNaFTtkJ44FLlNPI%2FText-Path-Draw%3Fnode-id%3D0%253A1\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe> </div> </div> <p class=\"paragraph-4\">This is a Figma file, you can pan and zoom Inside of it.</p> <div data-w-id=\"bbadca1b-4cc5-fcd5-8746-173f2c7e4ad4\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"columns-7 w-row\"> <div class=\"column-17 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy1\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Pros</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Easy to use.<br>‍</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Intuitive.<br>‍</div> </div> </div> <div class=\"column-18 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Cons</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Difficult to control, hard to create a precise result.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Not editable, user needs to redraw from the beginning.</div> </div> </div> </div> <div data-w-id=\"3dfe1395-dffd-feac-644e-a81de44ea5b3\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-3-copy\"> <h1 class=\"heading-2-copy2-copy\">Concept 2: Text Path Presets</h1> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy\">Choose a path preset to create the path you wish. Click the back button to finish editing.</p> </div> <div data-w-id=\"b6dca8a5-95aa-7b35-808a-32725f200614\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"html-embed-2 w-embed w-iframe\"> <div class=\"center\"> <iframe style=\"border:none;\" onload=\"delayedLoad()\" width=\"100%\" max-width=\"700px\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.figma.com/embed?embed_host=share&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.figma.com%2Ffile%2FspvCKfrrlNdDpZxppsVMHE%2FText-Path-Presets%3Fnode-id%3D0%253A1\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div> </div> <div data-w-id=\"489077de-e55c-8002-d067-0e324f215d38\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"columns-7 w-row\"> <div class=\"column-17 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy1\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Pros</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Easy to use.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Real time text preview.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Fast. A desired result can be achieved in one click.</div> </div> </div> <div class=\"column-18 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Cons</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Limited. Not customizable.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\"><br>‍</div> </div> </div> </div> <div data-w-id=\"143e1fdd-713e-5aef-80b7-4b3576e4aa8f\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-3-copy\"> <h1 class=\"heading-2-copy2-copy\">Concept 3: Dragging the text path </h1> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy\">Use circle shaped anchors to adjust the text path. There will be a slider giving the user a range between 3 to 7 control points. Dragging each anchor will adjust the look of the text. Use the undo/redo buttons in case of mistakes.</p> </div> <div data-w-id=\"56f4ac90-45c1-523b-aceb-2724d96b7f73\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"html-embed-2 w-embed w-iframe\"> <div class=\"center\"> <iframe style=\"border:none;\" onload=\"delayedLoad()\" width=\"100%\" max-width=\"700px\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.figma.com/embed?embed_host=share&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.figma.com%2Ffile%2FAIHL8DLJcUmF4o2BelnKhs%2FText-Path-Dots%3Fnode-id%3D0%253A1\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe> </div> </div> <p class=\"paragraph-4\">This is a Figma file, you can pan and zoom Inside of it.</p> <div data-w-id=\"04fc7dc0-ee4c-802c-d0dd-7551930ca9c9\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"columns-7 w-row\"> <div class=\"column-17 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy1\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Pros</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Intuitive.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Easy to use.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Customizable.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Real time text preview.</div> </div> </div> <div class=\"column-18 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Cons</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Finger may hide the text while editing.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> </div> </div> <div data-w-id=\"a9c5a15b-ce52-fe0d-14d3-cdd79ddcd6d3\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"div-block-3-copy\"> <h1 class=\"heading-2-copy2-copy\">Final Thoughts</h1> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy\">After researching the subject and designing the wireframes, I realized that combining the last two concepts would provide the best of both worlds: Preset options and full customization through circle shaped anchors.</p> </div> <div data-w-id=\"6bab417d-e782-69de-40a2-7523db1e1d8c\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"html-embed-2 w-embed w-iframe\"> <div class=\"center\"> <iframe style=\"border:none;\" onload=\"delayedLoad()\" width=\"100%\" max-width=\"700px\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://www.figma.com/embed?embed_host=share&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.figma.com%2Ffile%2F5fM15FwJyTPrBOb2z0RKzL%2FText-Path-Dots-and-Preset%3Fnode-id%3D0%253A1\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe> </div> </div> <div data-w-id=\"9ce0ea09-e4c5-6bc3-546a-98d621a56710\" style=\"opacity:0\" class=\"columns-7 w-row\"> <div class=\"column-17 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy1\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Pros</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Easy to use.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Customizable.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Intuitive.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">A desired result can be achieved in one click.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Real time text preview.</div> </div> </div> <div class=\"column-18 w-col w-col-6\"> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Cons</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block\">Finger may hide the text while editing.</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> <div class=\"div-block-20-copy\"> <div class=\"text-block-copy\">;</div> </div> </div> </div> <p class=\"paragraph-2-copy-copy9\">After taking into account all of the options, I created the following prototype, using the design system of the Enlight Photofox app (originally the task was given from them).</p><img src=\"/52cdf78ea948a046119840e69dd06849.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-23\"> <div class=\"div-block-18\"> <h6 class=\"heading-6\">Thanks for watching</h6> <div class=\"html-embed-3 w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"23\" height=\"23\" fill=\"red\" stroke=\"red\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z\"></path></svg>  </div> </div> </div> </div> <div></div> <script src=\"https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.4.1.min.220afd743d.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha256-CSXorXvZcTkaix6Yvo6HppcZGetbYMGWSFlBw8HfCJo=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <script src=\"/a6d6690ead3649be0b4ee71c1b08ba49.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>   <script>function o() {\n  window.frames